        "subject": "LU-3467 ost: use OBD_ALLOC_LARGE in ost_tls_get()",
        "message": "LU-3467 ost: use OBD_ALLOC_LARGE in ost_tls_get()\n\nThis patch replaces OBD_ALLOC_PTR with OBD_ALLOC_LARGE\nin ost_tls_get() and ost_io_thread_init() to allocate\nlarge buffer. The patch also replaces OBD_FREE_PTR with\nOBD_FREE_LARGE in ost_tls_put() and ost_io_thread_done().\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5d06ab08a83efb6dff87970a1b1a2d6c5f633cae\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_5"
    }
